    specialAbilities: "Talz Senses: Muftak's four eyes provide exceptional low-light vision. He receives +2D to Perception rolls in darkness or dim lighting.\n\nNative Cold Adaptation: Talz are adapted to arctic environments. Muftak suffers −1D to Strength and Stamina in extreme heat (like Tatooine's desert regions).\n\nFur Camouflage: In snow or pale-lit environments, Muftak's white fur grants +1D to sneak and hide.",
