    specialAbilities: "Chadra-Fan Size: Kabe is tiny — roughly 1 meter tall. She receives +2D to hide and sneak in environments with furniture or crowds, but suffers −1D to Strength-based damage in combat.\n\nKeen Senses: Chadra-Fan have exceptional hearing and smell. +1D to Perception rolls involving sound or scent.\n\nNimble Fingers: +1D to pick pocket and security beyond listed skill dice.",
