    specialAbilities: "Equipped with: broad-band antenna (intercepts/decodes standard-frequency comms); flamethrower (3D); long-range sensor (+2D search, 50–750m); movement sensor (+2D search for moving objects); sonic stunner (4D stun); grenade launcher (5D). Size: 2 meters.",
