    equipment: "Headset comlink, blaster pistol (4D damage), datapad",
    capsule: "A pale near-Human of indeterminable heritage, Putten's gray skin and large ears have attracted quite a few stares over the years. Putten has always been an outcast. Eventually, she wound up in Mos Eisley, and decided to take up residence and find a job here. Gruff, demanding and abrasive, she does have a few close friends; everyone else is greeted with boundless hostility. Her objective is to be obnoxious and demanding up to the very limit of her target's patience.",
    source: "WEG40069 Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley p.15"
