    capsule: "A 2.8-meter-tall insectoid, Sinthia Pulchatt is a member of the Kibnon species, a distant relative of the Verpine. Kibnon are green in color and look similar to a praying mantis, with bulbous eyes atop a slender stalk. Their four legs aid in stability to support their slender thorax and abdomen, and their arms are usually held up close to their bodies. Pulchatt is one of many Mos Eisley spice merchants, preened for this position at an early age. She fulfills her duties without question as a liaison between Jabba and her boss, whose name she won't reveal. She projects a kind and lofty attitude, exotic-looking enough to parlay that into a conversation starter — but she is always looking for new spice customers, regardless of the harm the spice will do.",
