    specialAbilities: "Vision: Trandoshan vision operates in the infrared spectrum, allowing them to see in darkness with no penalty.\nClumsy: Trandoshans lack manual dexterity. -2D penalty to actions requiring precise finger movement (picking locks, picking pockets, etc.).",
