    specialAbilities: "Natural Body Armor: Horny keratin scales provide +2D against physical attacks and +1D against energy attacks.\nRadiation Resistance: Natural resistance to most forms of radiation. +2D when defending against radiation effects.\nVision: Can see in the infrared spectrum, allowing sight in complete darkness provided there are heat sources.",
