    capsule: "Carn'ar is a young Aqualish female and a victim in her own right. The eldest child of an impoverished family, embittered by the cruelty of her childhood, she turned to bounty hunting to support her family and vent her anger. She has become increasingly cruel and uncaring, enjoying capturing those too weak to protect themselves. Her trademark is insistence on using primitive projectile weapons instead of blasters. After every successful hunt, she sends an engraved shell casing to the victim's family as a 'reminder' of her victory.",
