    capsule: "H'rinnrada is a Rodian hunter who accurately represents the values of her species: she revels in the hunt and sees other sapients as mere targets. Obsessed with gaining status in her clan and dreams of founding her own clan one day. Never to be trusted — known to turn on employers as soon as she has collected a bounty. Prefers a modified blaster rifle and neurostaff. Not one for subtlety: she publicly attacks targets, intent on building a fearsome reputation.",
    source: "WEG40073 Galaxy Guide 10: Bounty Hunters p.77"
