    specialAbilities: "Senses: Weak long-distance vision (+10 difficulty beyond 15m), but excellent close range — eyes, smell, and heat-sensing bulb provide +1D Perception within 15m using heat, smell, or movement.\nThick Hide: +1D Strength vs physical attacks (not energy).\nTalons: +1D to climbing, Strength (combat), or digging.\nSalt Weakness: Salt-addicted. Must consume salt once a day or suffer -1D to all actions.",
