    capsule: "Garim was the warden of an Imperial prison until a Rebel assault team raided the installation and freed all his charges. Resigning in disgrace, he has vowed never to rest until he returns all escaped prisoners to Imperial custody. He cut a deal with House Tresario — the guild receives a substantial percentage of bounties in exchange for aid and equipment. Modestly successful to date. Self-centered, moody, and withdrawn, he constantly broods about his self-determined mission.",
