    capsule: "Following a pirate attack on her family's transport, Janildakara was sold to Zygerian slavers. After years of suffering she escaped, but was unable to locate her parents (still undetermined). She joined House Renliss believing the guild could help find her family. She has developed a keen interest in poisoning with a marked aptitude for creating imaginative toxins. Her superiors have exploited her deep-seated hatred and resentments, manufacturing an excellent tool for their own ends. A young Human female barely out of adolescence, she wears an armored half-vest and stun cloak and relies on poison-coated throwing knives. She bears a prominent brand on her neck — the mark of her Zygerian slave masters.",
