    capsule: "Of all the reasons to prey on another sentient, Wexlann's is certainly among the more unusual. A devotee of fine art and rare collectables, he takes special assignments to support his personal art collection. When he learns of a rare work up for sale, his agents bid on it and he goes on a hunt to raise the credits. While he has a substantial family fortune, he chooses to hunt as a means of 'earning' his treasures. His current collection is valued at over two million credits.",
