    capsule: "To most, Dalmeidan appears to be a minor planetary bureaucrat. His friends consider him a lonely, unhappy man dominated by a demanding spouse. Few are aware that this seemingly inconsequential administrator is a proficient bounty hunter living a disturbing, almost comic double life. He uses his position within the Imperial bureaucracy to get information, occasionally going on long 'business trips' to conduct hunts. His earnings have been hidden away — eventually, when the time is right, Dalmeidan will take that one long business trip and leave his mundane existence for good.",
