    capsule: "Ravallian Dast accepts only illegal contracts — her reasoning is that the Empire is an illegal and immoral government, making its laws invalid. She works primarily for the Rebel Alliance, though she doesn't perform charity and expects to be paid well. The Alliance has been willing to spend precious credits for her skills — she has captured at least five top Imperial officials and advisors. When not working for the Alliance, she accepts assignments from private citizens needing services without Imperial scrutiny. She carefully reviews each assignment against her own moral code. Though seriously wounded several times, she refuses to leave the business — her only goal is utterly destroying the Empire and its supporters.",
    source: "WEG40073 Galaxy Guide 10: Bounty Hunters p.81"
