    capsule: "Malak loves violence. This, combined with a basic dislike of non-Rodians, makes her an ideal candidate for her position. Malak enjoys leading raids against unsuspecting communities far removed from any protection. She is in the business solely for the money and gives little thought to the ultimate disposition of those whose lives she disrupts so completely. TracSheet: Shows little concern for damaging merchandise during acquisition. Specializes in private commissions for the delivery of 'specialty goods.' Several head spines missing, fingers typically adorned with numerous expensive rings.",
