    capsule: "Colonel Bren Derlin is one of the more famous Republic officers. He led the Rebel commandos in the assault on the Imperial bunker on Endor, was an important part of Echo Base command on Hoth, and saved countless civilian lives at the Battle of Nentan. Few know he is the son of Senator Galen Derlin, a close friend of Bail Organa who was murdered by an Imperial assassin. Incensed at his father's political execution, Bren joined the Rebel Alliance as an infantry soldier, rising through the ranks due to his tactical ability. Now part of the tactical defense force on Coruscant, placed there partly for his ability and partly at Leia Organa Solo's insistence. A quiet, unassuming man in his early fifties, he has earned the loyalty of every soldier who has served under his command.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.36"
