    equipment: "New Republic security uniform, encoded datapad (containing detailed information on security arrangements in Imperial Palace on Coruscant), secure comlink, heavy blaster pistol (5D)",
    capsule: "Colonel Jak Bremen grew up on Shiffrin in the Outer Rim. His father Kallin, the village chief constable, was executed by Imperial forces along with a group of peaceful protesters after their land was confiscated for hfredium mining. Jak fled off-world and settled on Coveway, becoming the colonists' constable and marrying a local woman. When an Imperial garrison destroyed his village and killed his wife and infant daughter, he joined a Rebel strike team to neutralize the base. He rose through Alliance ranks from security officer to security chief of the cruiser Starveil. After Endor, he was promoted to Director of Security for the New Republic Council. A martinet who always follows the rule book, he is often at odds with unorthodox strategists like Han Solo and Garm Bel Iblis. He tightened Imperial Palace security considerably after an Imperial strike team infiltrated the building.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.37"
