    equipment: "New Republic captain's uniform, datapad, comlink, blaster pistol (4D)",
    capsule: "Captain Afyon was a young man during the Clone Wars, following Bail Organa of Alderaan to war. Like Leia Organa, he was off-planet when the Death Star destroyed Alderaan. Princess Leia rallied her people, and Afyon answered the call, becoming first officer aboard a Corellian gunship and eventually earning his own command. Now captain of the escort frigate Larkhess, he has been hauling cargo for nearly a year to stimulate galactic trade, forced to operate his 920-crew ship with just 15 men. Tired, frustrated, and jealous of the starfighter hotshots who lounge on his ship, he nonetheless proved his worth at Sluis Van — when stormtroopers boarded, he was prepared to destroy the Larkhess rather than let it fall into Imperial hands.",
