    capsule: "Hobbie Klivian has led an active life since joining the Rebellion. After graduating from the Imperial Academy, he jumped ship with Biggs Darklighter and ran guns for the Alliance near Sullust. He was Luke Skywalker's wingman at Echo Base on Hoth, and after the base fell he flew regular missions with Rogue Squadron. Well known for both his considerable piloting ability and his considerable sarcasm and skepticism. Tall — just shy of 2 meters — and very slender, with dirty blond hair, brown eyes, and a perpetually bland expression. Known for his slightly negative attitude and secretly very nervous for the safety of other squadron members during missions.",
