    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D), Imperial Navy uniform, comlink, datapad",
    capsule: "Captain Dorja commands the Imperial Star Destroyer Relentless since before the Battle of Endor, where his ship suffered no casualties — though some attribute this to his cautious command style and reluctance to engage directly. He comes from a family with a rich tradition in Imperial and Old Republic military life stretching back six generations. He almost refused to follow Pellaeon's command after Endor and has plotted to seize power himself, but Grand Admiral Thrawn's return ended those ambitions. Dorja despises Thrawn for being non-human and resents the Relentless being left out of Thrawn's personal armada. His failure to capture Solo and Skywalker at New Cov has not gone unnoticed. He keeps his head low, waiting for an opportunity to reinstate the New Order in all its undiluted glory.",
    source: "WEG40131 The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook p.67"
