    capsule: "Imperial Intelligence solo operatives are the lone wolves who can be trusted to operate effectively even when completely cut off from contact with higher authorities. Highly trained and dedicated, these operatives are considered 'super agents' by COMPNOR and the other arms of Imperial Intelligence. Often, solo Intel agents were recruited by the Emperor to serve as his 'Hands.' Solo operatives were answerable only to the Emperor and a few of his top advisors. They handle espionage, covert intelligence gathering, extraction or execution of possible security risks, and procurement of needed technology.",
