    specialAbilities: "Some skills marked with * have been artificially enhanced by specialized training and mnemiotic drugs. Intel teams usually include at least one communications specialist (communications 9D), one heavy weapons specialist (blaster: heavy blaster 10D, blaster: blaster rifle 10D, blaster artillery 10D, missile weapons 9D), and one scout specialist (search 10D, search: tracking 10D+1, sneak 10D).",
