    move: 9,
    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D)",
    capsule: "Ellor left his homeworld Duro looking for excitement. He encountered a young Talon Karrde, who convinced the naive Duro to help with a smuggling job. Their first venture nearly ended in disaster when an Interdictor cruiser appeared, but Karrde's near-suicidal maneuvers shook off the pursuers. Ellor was terrified but exhilarated, and has remained a smuggler to this day. He is tall and thin, with large eyes, no nose, and a thin slit of a mouth. Extremely reckless, though his experiences with Karrde have tempered his rashness. Karrde worries that Ellor's impulsiveness will someday cost the Duro his life.",
