    specialAbilities: "Energy Sensitivity: Gotals receive +3D to search in wide open areas. Mood Detection: Gotals can read the moods of others. Fast Initiative: Gotals who are not suffering from radiation static receive a +1D bonus when rolling initiative against non-Gotal opponents.",
