    specialAbilities: "Cyborg Brain: Yaka have implanted cyborg brains that greatly increase their intelligence (Luwingo's stats reflect this surgery). All Yaka learn and improve Knowledge and Technical skills at half the normal cost.",
    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 6,
