    capsule: "Romort Raort is a being of simple pleasures: he just likes seeing people suffer. Whether it was as a bully on his homeworld of Irith shaking down kids for their lunch money, or today as a spice-jacker, Romort is a brute who really likes his job. He first started out as a kneebreaker for the old Elaginn gang of jackers, but since Elaginn had that terrible accident — flexi-pasting himself to a chair and jumping out a window — Romort has had to run things. Through determination and cruelty, he built up the old gang into one of the biggest spice-jacking rings in Hutt space. He has contacts in port authorities on dozens of worlds; by calling a few friends, he can track large spice shipments. Using an ion cannon 'donated' by some Rebel gunrunners, it's an easy matter to hit a ship while in dock and strip it of cargo while the crew is readied for sale to slavers.",
