    move: 8,
    equipment: "Blaster rifle (5D+1), detonite (10 charges, 5D each), blast armor (+2D+2 physical, +1D energy, -1D DEX and related skills; internal comlink; sealed enviro/atmosphere system; concealed forearm-mounted vibroknives STR+1D, uses melee combat, Easy difficulty; heat projector 5D to anyone touching armor, 2 rounds only), 3 medpacs, 2 weeks rations, 3 pairs magbinders, 750 credits",
    capsule: "Dyyz Nataz rose through the ranks of his system's police forces with a reputation for a tough-as-nails manner and a way of dealing with violent sociopaths. Assigned the rank of Sector Ranger, he ran across Goa during a case. The two teamed up to infiltrate the hideout of a counterfeit credit ring on an abandoned ore freighter, not suspecting it was a setup by Jabba the Hutt. Ambushed by Gank Killers, they endured hours of torture. When the Ganks made them play sabacc to decide who died first, their partner Thaffe intentionally threw the game to save Goa. As they shot Thaffe, Goa went berserk and freed himself; Nataz broke free as well and they destroyed the Ganks. They set the freighter on a collision course with Jabba's in-system palace asteroid, earning Nataz the nickname 'Megadeath.' Relieved of duty in the scandal, they easily handled the bounty hunters Jabba sent after them, recycled the gear, and became bounty hunters themselves.",
